github.setup        cooljeanius cec 0.4 v
categories          lang
platforms           darwin
maintainers         gwmail.gwu.edu:egall
license             BSD 3-clause

description         The Columbia Esterel Compiler

long_description    ${description}. Warning: doesn't actually work yet

homepage            http://www.cs.columbia.edu/~sedwards/cec/

